{"tid":302693,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[連坐法] 青年被指塗鴉不認罪  警察拘捕家人迫認罪","createTime":"2017-06-29T14:40:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T06:05:55.000Z","uid":7025,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"931968bd25c56a288a60c1f90b2d73db255010cf","tid":302693,"uid":7025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T14:40:43.000Z","msg":"【青年被指塗鴉不認罪  警察拘捕家人迫認罪】<br />\n<br />\n今晨九時，一名本土民主前線成員涉嫌因塗鴉而被警方以「刑事毀壞」罪名拘捕，現被還押於九龍城警署。<br />\n<br />\n根據消息，警方曾要求該被捕成員招認控罪，其後更威脅該成員若不認罪將拘捕其家人。其後律師證實青年父親及家弟被捕，警方亦正搜捕其母親，現已有律師跟進。<br />\n<br />\n本土民主前線強烈譴責警方濫用職權，剝奪被捕人士之基本人權。敝黨懷疑警方因中共領導來港在即而清洗太平地，甚至藉「連坐法」營造白色恐怖，恫嚇本土派人士。敝黨呼籲社會各界密切關注，並於未來數日保持警惕，敝黨不排除將有進一步行動。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/19511579_1924318664488703_8026889743533696924_n.jpg?oh=42fae92fb1cb7410b3fa6edf4b2bdb0b&amp;oe=5A11205C\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F19511579_1924318664488703_8026889743533696924_n.jpg%3Foh%3D42fae92fb1cb7410b3fa6edf4b2bdb0b%26oe%3D5A11205C&h=ec1ede64&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"648310fd973acf302fa29fa78942fb36ef3b674b","tid":302693,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T14:41:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/29/215419_7b24aa09a208a123d239459d05c16aad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F29%2F215419_7b24aa09a208a123d239459d05c16aad.jpg&h=26ef0569&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d69b987668dd7f6b70b2682ab0366ed7d2b62d3f","tid":302693,"uid":36029,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T14:44:41.000Z","msg":"有一天，世界上要推出全世界最厲害的警察。 <br />\n到了最後一個階段，剩下 一個美國的FBI、 蘇俄的KGB及中國的公安。 <br />\n考題是放一隻小白兔進一 個不小的森林， <br />\n要在十分鐘之內把目標（小白兔）找出來，否則就淘汰。 <br />\n首先，FBI 進去了，展開地毯式的搜索， <br />\n十分鐘過去了，FBI 毫無所獲。下一個是KGB，<br />\n一進去就放火燒林，企圖逼出小白兔，十分鐘過去了， <br />\n燒林的效果沒想像中大， KGB也被淘汰了。 <br />\n輪到了中國的公安，只見他不慌不忙的晃著手上的警棍進了森林。 <br />\n不到五分鐘的時間，中國公安出來了，手上擰著一隻熊貓的耳朵， <br />\n帶了一隻熊貓出來。 正當大家覺得奇怪時， <br />\n熊貓說話了： 不要再打了！不要再打了！我承認我是小白兔！"},{"pid":"ad43aa00782346cb366507b09e3a5df832dab926","tid":302693,"uid":7025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T14:51:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bef1f8b787f0d0dc813d90b3750f510629ede654","tid":302693,"uid":36178,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T15:10:11.000Z","msg":"老屈唔成就抄家, 呢個係咩撚嘢香港"},{"pid":"25fc38e68ba673dae13d5cafac946d1445425595","tid":302693,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T16:02:20.000Z","msg":"開始鳥 連坐"},{"pid":"c467dc77b6e8a1fa649b6c45044c4ce9ece9cb3b","tid":302693,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T16:06:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20429ca2d50834b6db1940a88788f5f3330d6d4a","tid":302693,"uid":10679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T16:08:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a2c8d40065cb04a7f52fe1dcdcebba5ca4c213e","tid":302693,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T22:59:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"760a6f71d2fe3b0720de62b8b8bedfece867b09f","tid":302693,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T23:41:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a9f1e110b3318c03cd5a9d73a3c6c00b3d212efe","tid":302693,"uid":259993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:05:55.000Z","msg":"警隊必須重組<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}